        <a id="top"></a>
        <div id="siteNotice" class="mw-body-content"><div id="localNotice" lang="zh-Hans-CN" dir="ltr"><div class="hidden-xs sitenotice-background" style="text-align:center; padding: 20px 0px; line-height: 25px;border-radius: 6px;box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px #ddd;">
<p><b style="color:#857366;">台词试听功能</b>(<a href="/sgs/%E6%AD%A6%E5%B0%86%E5%9B%BE%E9%89%B4" title="武将图鉴">武将</a>/<a href="/sgs/%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4" title="皮肤">皮肤</a>/<a href="/sgs/%E5%B0%86%E7%81%B5%E5%9B%BE%E9%89%B4" title="将灵图鉴">将灵</a>)已上线，在对应页面的台词板块即可试听<br />目前音频功能仍有缺失或错误的情况，可点击<a href="/sgs/%E4%B8%89%E5%9B%BD%E6%9D%80BWIKI%E5%8F%8D%E9%A6%88%E6%9D%BF" title="三国杀BWIKI反馈板"><font color="#857366">反馈</font></a>提醒我们<br />有兴趣参与编辑的请点击下方企鹅群加入我们哦～<br />
欢迎收藏起来防止迷路，按"Ctrl+D"收藏本站哦~(´▽`ʃ♡ƪ)！<br />
<img alt="标题左窗格.png" src="https://patchwiki.biligame.com/images/sgs/6/6e/49l0bf09kdmtwrnlu918c64shmi06bx.png" decoding="async" width="100" height="20" data-file-width="100" data-file-height="20" />✬<img alt="标题右窗格.png" src="https://patchwiki.biligame.com/images/sgs/0/05/1jumtaie3e4htkd6x711g9ak88js3py.png" decoding="async" width="100" height="20" data-file-width="100" data-file-height="20" /><br />
</p>
<div class="hlist" style="text-align:center;"><li><a href="/sgs/%E4%B8%89%E5%9B%BD%E6%9D%80BWIKI%E5%8F%8D%E9%A6%88%E6%9D%BF" title="三国杀BWIKI反馈板"><font color="#857366">反馈</font></a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://game.bilibili.com/linkfilter/?url=https://jq.qq.com/?_wv=1027&amp;k=qMqAyKnZ" target="_blank"><font color="#857366"><i class="fa-qq fab" style="font-size:10px;color:;"></i>485385329</font></a></li><li><a href="/sgs/%E4%B8%89%E5%9B%BD%E6%9D%80WIKI%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B" class="mw-redirect" title="三国杀WIKI编辑教程"><font color="#857366">教程</font></a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://wiki.biligame.com/msgs/"><font color="#857366">三国杀移动版WIKI</font></a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://wiki.biligame.com/sgsol/"><font color="#857366">三国杀ONLINEWIKI</font></a></li></div>
</div>
<div class="top-tg visible-xs" style="text-align:left; color:#333;line-height: 24px;padding:10px; background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);border-radius: 6px;box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px #ddd;"><b style="color:#857366;">台词试听功能</b>(<a href="/sgs/%E6%AD%A6%E5%B0%86%E5%9B%BE%E9%89%B4" title="武将图鉴">武将</a>/<a href="/sgs/%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4" title="皮肤">皮肤</a>/<a href="/sgs/%E5%B0%86%E7%81%B5%E5%9B%BE%E9%89%B4" title="将灵图鉴">将灵</a>)已上线，在对应页面的台词板块即可试听；目前音频功能仍有缺失或错误的情况，可点击<a href="/sgs/%E4%B8%89%E5%9B%BD%E6%9D%80BWIKI%E5%8F%8D%E9%A6%88%E6%9D%BF" title="三国杀BWIKI反馈板"><font color="#857366">反馈</font></a>提醒我们；有兴趣参与编辑的请点击下方企鹅群加入我们哦～。欢迎<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://wiki.biligame.com/wiki/BWIKI%E6%94%B6%E8%97%8F%E5%88%B0%E6%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2%E7%9A%84%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E"><font color="#857366">收藏</font></a>起来防止迷路~(´▽`ʃ♡ƪ)！<br />
<hr /><div class="hlist" style="text-align:center;"><li><a href="/sgs/%E4%B8%89%E5%9B%BD%E6%9D%80BWIKI%E5%8F%8D%E9%A6%88%E6%9D%BF" title="三国杀BWIKI反馈板"><font color="#857366">反馈</font></a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://game.bilibili.com/linkfilter/?url=https://jq.qq.com/?_wv=1027&amp;k=qMqAyKnZ" target="_blank"><font color="#857366"><i class="fa-qq fab" style="font-size:10px;color:;"></i>485385329</font></a></li><li><a href="/sgs/%E4%B8%89%E5%9B%BD%E6%9D%80WIKI%E7%BC%96%E8%BE%91%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B" class="mw-redirect" title="三国杀WIKI编辑教程"><font color="#857366">教程</font></a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://wiki.biligame.com/msgs/"><font color="#857366">三国杀移动版WIKI</font></a></li><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://wiki.biligame.com/sgsol/"><font color="#857366">三国杀ONLINEWIKI</font></a></li></div>

<div class="glossy-white-bg-light flex-container full-width between-on-x-axis" style="margin-bottom:5px;"><div style="flex: 1;overflow: hidden;text-overflow: ellipsis;white-space: nowrap;"><a href="/sgs/%E9%A6%96%E9%A1%B5" title="首页">首页</a> &gt; <a href="/sgs/%E6%AD%A6%E5%B0%86" title="武将">武将</a> <span style="writing-mode: tb-rl;">&gt;</span></div>

<script>
if(hasInput !== "") setTimeout(function(){$("#titles").parent().show();$("#titles").val(titles)}, 1000)
function Purge(){

	window.titleArray = titles.replaceAll(", ", ",").split(",");
   console.log(titles)
	if(hasInput !== "") window.titleArray = $("#titles").val().replace(/、/g, ",").replace(/, /, ",").split(",");
	window.pageIndex = 0;
   window.pageIndex2 = 0;
   
  var ParseArray = getNewArray(titleArray,50);
  
   console.log(ParseArray);
   
   ParseArray.forEach(function(value,index,array) {
    new mw.Api().post({
		"action": "purge",
		"format": "json",
		"titles": value.join("|")
	}).then(index == array.length - 1 ? getPage : console.log(index));
})
	
}
function getNewArray(array, subGroupLength) {
  let index = 0;
  let newArray = [];
  while(index < array.length) {
      newArray.push(array.slice(index, index += subGroupLength));
  }
  return newArray;
}
function getPage(){
	$.get(mw.config.get("wgCookiePath") + titleArray[pageIndex++]).then(function(){
   document.getElementById("refresh").innerHTML ="▶ 正在处理"+ (1 + pageIndex2++) +"/"+titleArray.length;
	if(pageIndex2 >= titleArray.length)
    {
    setTimeout(function(){alert("刷新完毕");document.getElementById("refresh").innerHTML ="▶ 刷新技能页";},10);
    } 
    })
	if(pageIndex >= titleArray.length)
    {
    return;
    } 
	setTimeout(getPage,50)
}
</script>

<script>
  var inputx;
  function doQuickTab(tab)
  {
      
    if(tab=="清空")
      tab=null;
    else
    if(tab.parentElement)
    tab = $(tab.parentElement).children("input").val();
    
    var scroll=document.body.scrollTop;
    inputx.each(function(){
      $(this).attr("readonly",true);
      this.focus({preventScroll:true});
 
//alert("focus");     
      $(this).val("").attr("readonly",false);
      
      if(!tab) 
      {
document.execCommand("inserttext",false,' ');
        $(this).val("");
      }else
 document.execCommand("inserttext",false,tab);
      // alert("insert"); 
    $(this).blur();
    document.body.scrollTop = scroll;
    });
    
   
    //$("select").change();
   // alert(tab);
    
}

    $(document).ready(function(){  
      
      if(quickTab!="")
  {
    quickTab="清空,"+quickTab;
    quickTab = quickTab.replace(/\s*/g,"").split(",");  
    
    
  for(var i=0;i<quickTab.length;i++)
  {
    if(quickTab[i] != "")
  $("#quickTab").append(`<button class="${quickTab[i] =="清空"?"btn label label-danger" : "btn btn-default"}" onclick="doQuickTab('${quickTab[i]}')">${quickTab[i]}</button>`);
  }
  }
//sgs_AJAX();
    });
    
}]);

if(!sort)
{
sort="创建日期"
}
var count = 0;
var last_count = 0;
var cur_count = 0;
var $Tables;
var wjNames;
var pageNames;
var button;
var item;

window.Length = 0;

var test;
test=GetButton();

function GetButton(){
console.log("获取按钮");
button=document.getElementsByClassName(sort + " sorting");
console.log("获取长度"+button.length);
Length=button.length;
if(button.length==0)
{
console.log("GetButton False!!");
setTimeout(GetButton,500);
}
else 
{
var datatable = $(".datatable.display.dataTable.no-footer"); 

datatable.css("min-width",datatableOverFlowWidth);

datatable.after($("<div class=\"datatableOverFlow\" style=\"overflow-x:auto;width:100%;\"></div>"))

datatable.each(function(index,domEle){
$(domEle).next().append($(domEle));
})

var links = $(".smw-datatable-toolbar").find("li > a");
links.each(function(index,domEle){
$(domEle).attr("href",$(domEle).attr("href") + "&p%5Bbom%5D=yes")
})

    $(document).on("click", ".下载 > a", function(event) {
        event.preventDefault();
           var downloadFile = function(url, filename){
		fetch(url)
	        .then(response => response.blob())
	        .then(blob => {
	            var a = document.createElement('a');
	            a.download = filename;
	            a.href = window.URL.createObjectURL(blob);
	            document.body.appendChild(a); // for firefox
	            a.click();    
	            a.remove();         
	        });
    }

    downloadFile($(this).attr("href"),$(this).find(".皮肤信息").attr("data-name"));
    });

inputx = $(".dataTables_filter > * > input");
inputx.css("-webkit-user-select","auto");
 inputx.css("background","white");
  if(inputx.length>1 &quickTab!="")
    inputx.parent().append(`<button class="btn-xs btn-default" onclick="doQuickTab(this)">搜他表</button>`);
 
Click();

$Tables = $("table.datatable");
$(".dataTables_filter").find("input").each(function(){

this.placeholder = "数据表工具v1.0";
});

sgs_AJAX($Tables);

// 监听dom变动
var tt_Observer = new MutationObserver(function(mutationsList){
 sgs_AJAX($Tables);
});
	
$("table.datatable").children("tbody").each(function(){

tt_Observer.observe(this, {
		childList: true, // 监视节点增删事件
		subtree: false // 包含所有后代节点（而不只是子节点）
});

});

return 1;
}
}

function Click(){
if(noclick)
return;
for (Index = 0; Index < Length; Index++)
{
item=button[0];
item.click();
item.click();
console.log("点击"+(Index+1));
}
}


function AJAX2($list,tb,ta,fade = true)
{
var textList = [];

$list.each(function(i,e){

var txt;

if(Array.isArray(tb))
txt = "{"+ "{" + "#show:" +  tb[i] + "|?" + ta + "}}";
else
txt = tb + $(e).text() + ta;

if(!$(e).attr("ajax") && $(e).html() && !$(e).html().replaceAll("<br>","").replace(/<span class="highlight">[^<]+<\/span>/g,"").match(/<[^>]+>/gi))
textList.push(txt);
else
textList.push("");

});

if(textList.join("")=="")
{
//console.log("无需处理");
return;
}

count++;

var parse = textList.join("<hr>") + "<hr>";

$list.attr("ajax","1");
console.log(textList);

$.getJSON( mw.util.wikiScript( 'api'), {
		format: 'json',
		action: 'parse',
		text: parse,
		contentmodel: 'wikitext'
	}).fail(function(error){ // 辣鸡解析器，不让我直接.catch
      $list.attr("ajax","");
		AJAX($list,tb,ta,fade);        
	 }).done( function ( data ) {
      
    if(fade) $list.fadeOut(0);
       var dataTxt = data.parse.text["*"];
       var $html = $(dataTxt);

   //console.log($html.html().split("<hr>"));
        
   $html.html().split("<hr>").forEach(function(e,i){
//console.log(e);
    e = pout(e);

    if(e.replaceAll("<p></p>","").replace(/[\r\n]/g, '') == "")
    {
    if(fade) $list.eq(i).fadeIn(0);
    }else
    {
    $list.eq(i).html(e);
    if(fade) $list.eq(i).fadeIn();
    //console.log(e);
     }
    });  
    
   UpdateInput();

	});

}

function sgs_AJAX($tbs)
{
//console.log($tbs);

$tbs.each(function(){

var pageNames = [];

$(this).find("td.页面名").each(function(){
pageNames.push($(this).text());
});

AJAX2($(this).find("td.所属武将"),"{"+ "{" + "头像|武将|小|","}}");
AJAX2($(this).find("td.画师"),"{"+ "{" + "画师|","}}",false);
//AJAX2($(this).find("td.画师"),pageNames,"画师展示",false);
AJAX2($(this).find("td.皮肤名"),pageNames,"皮肤展示",false);
AJAX2($(this).find("td.技能"),pageNames,"悬浮技能",false);
AJAX2($(this).find("td.下载"),pageNames,"下载链接");
//if(count != 0)
//last_count = count;
//else
//count = last_count;

});

//showOther("td.下载","下载链接");
}

function UpdateInput()
{

cur_count++;
console.log(cur_count + ":" + count);
if(cur_count >= count)
{
cur_count = 0;
count = 0;
$("select").change();
}

this.dispatchEvent(new MouseEvent('click', {
    bubbles: true,
    cancelable: true,
    view: window,
    shiftKey: true,
    button:0,
    buttons:0
}));
});*/

//$("th.高亮修正").click();


}

function pout(txt)
{
//①是“一”个标签  ②该标签是p
if($(txt) && $("<div>" + txt + "</div>").children().length == 1 && txt.replace($(txt).html(),"") == "<p></p>")
return $(txt).html();
else
return txt;
}

</style>
